<p>Recapping ! Each Developer <strong>MUST</strong> follow the next principle:<br />
<em>Always code as if the person who ends up maintaining your code is a violent psychopath who knows where you live.</em></p>

<p>Don’t reinvent the wheel there are a couple of standards out there for many years which are held for a good reason.</p>

<p>Happy code formatting :D</p>

